  "text": "We were not aware of this work when we developed the UTCP theory in this paper, but there are very strong parallels between the features of our semantics and those in [CITATION_1] . In some sense our semantics is a re-working of his within UTP. We shall point out specific correspondences as we proceed with our presentation.",
